tterindia.com%2F264378%2Fkarma-sonam-natwest-group-earth-heroes-award-snow-leopard-himalayan-wolf-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnow%20leopard%3C%2Fa%3E%20killing%20a%20mountain%20sheep%20or%20goat.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20herbivores%20feed%20on%20alpine%20pastures%20that%20grow%20on%20the%20slopes%20of%20the%20mountain%20ranges.%20By%20controlling%20the%20population%20of%20these%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20the%20snow%20leopard%20gives%20the%20grasses%20and%20plants%20a%20chance%20to%20regenerate%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Namgail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20issue%20the%20feline%20helps%20tackle%20is%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prevalence%20of%20natural%20disasters%20in%20the%20region%20is%20compounded%20by%20climate%20change.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20days%20we%20are%20receiving%20more%20rain%20and%20less%20snow.%20As%20the%20rainwater%20flows%20down%20the%20slopes%2C%20the%20loose%20soil%20also%20goes%20with%20it.%E2%80%9D%20Mind%20you%2C%20the%20soil%20is%20loosened%20by%20the%20grazing%20activity%20of%20the%20goats.%20The%20muddy%20water%20floods%20the%20villages%20destroying%20property%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20do%20you%20see%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F86991%2Fovercome-age-old-prejudices-snow-leopard-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20ecological%20linkage%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%E2%80%9D%20Namgail%20asks%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20moves%20on%20to%20explore%20the%20third%20benefit%20of%20having%20the%20animal%20in%20the%20region%20%E2%80%94%20enhancing%20carnivore%20diversity.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20snow%20leopard%E2%80%99s%20preferred%20prey%20are%20the%20Asiatic%20Ibex%20and%20the%20Himalayan%20Blue%20Sheep.%20Preying%20on%20these%20indirectly%20allows%20other%20species%20of%20sheep%20and%20goats%20to%20thrive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20question%20begs%20to%20be%20asked%3