uling%20the%20locals%E2%80%99%20livestock.%20And%20Namgail%20emphasises%20that%20this%20is%20where%20the%20conservancy%20steps%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20alongside%20the%20ferocious%20predator%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20dream%20for%20the%20pastoral%20communities%20of%20Ladakh.%20However%2C%20being%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F96401%2Fproject-shen-snow-leopard-conservation-women-handicrafts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaintain%20their%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20money%20they%20earn%20through%20protecting%20it%20serves%20as%20an%20incentive.%20In%20fact%2C%20once%20hailed%20as%20pests%2C%20Namgail%20says%20the%20felines%20are%20now%20fondly%20called%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERi%20Gyancha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98ornaments%20of%20the%20mountains%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20this%20nickname%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20soften%20the%20attitude%20of%20the%20snow%20leopard%20towards%20the%20locals%20who%20continue%20to%20see%20rare%20cases%20of%20their%20cattle%20being%20mauled%20and%20eaten.%20But%20at%20least%20now%2C%20they%20are%20reimbursed%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENamgail%20notes%20that%20the%20insurance%20model%20is%20only%20one%20of%20the%20many%20activities%20at%20the%20conservancy.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20focus%20on%20community-based%20tourism%2C%20education%20and%20research%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20and%20promotion%20of%20innovative%20grass-root%20measures%20that%20encourage%20local%20people%20to%20become%20better%20stewards%20of%20the%20endangered%20snow%20leopards%2C%20their%20prey%2C%20and%20habitats.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20arm%20of%20the%20conservancy%20is%20the%20award-winning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334115%2Fbest-homestays-in-himachal-pradesh-uttarakhand-to-enjoy-snowfall-in-winter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHimalayan%20Homestay%20Programme%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20was%20started%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Wangchuk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20tourism%20thrive%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarrating%20how%20it%20began%2C%20Namgail%20shares%20it%20was%20during%20a%20visit%20that%20he%20and%20Wangchuk%20made%20to%20the%20Hemis%20National%20Park%20in%20the%20year%202001.%20A%20conversation%20with%20one%20of%20the%20village%20women%20introduced%20them%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20community-led%20tourism.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20women%20suggested%20that%20since%20the%20tourist%20camps%20led%20to%20so%20much%20garbage%20being%20generated%2C%20why%20not%20let%20them%20live%20in%20the%20local%20homes%3F%E2%80%9D%20Namgail%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20weeks%20that%20followed%2C%20the%20duo%20went%20around%20the%20villages%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20surveyed%20the%20local%20communities%20to%20see%20if%20they%20were%20willing%20to%20host%20guests.%20They%20were%20elated.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20the%20homestay%20arm%20was%20born.%20Deachen%20who%20has%20also%20converted%20her%20home%20into%20a%20homestay%2C%20says%20she%20loves%20having%20tourists%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-9-1711368223.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20locals%20are%20now%20welcoming%20tourists%20into%20their%20home%20and%20giving%20them%20an%20authentic%20Ladakhi%20experience%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-9-1711368223.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-9-1711368223-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2