l%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331406%2Fwrestler-parmanand-jain-started-mahaveer-rabri-bhandar-became-iconic-eatery-of-jaipur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20afternoon%20experiment%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201868%20by%20a%20man%20named%20Nobin%20Chandra%20Das.%20Rolling%20balls%20of%20curdled%20milk%20and%20then%20boiling%20them%20in%20sugar%20syrup%20resulted%20in%20the%20beloved%20sweet%20that%20Kolkata%20and%20the%20globe%20adore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EForbes%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20even%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20was%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20place%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Erosogollas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20story%20is%20often%20retold%20of%20a%20time%20Tagore%20was%20served%20a%20pot%20of%20%3Cem%3Erosogollas%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20one%20of%20his%20acquaintances.%20Tagore%20nibbled%20at%20one%20and%20then%20asked%20if%20it%20was%20Das%20who%20had%20prepared%20these.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t.%20Tagore%20then%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20must%20feed%20me%20%3Cem%3Erosogollas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20make%20sure%20it%E2%80%99s%20from%20Nobin%E2%80%99s.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Balaram%20Mullick%20%26amp%3B%20Radharaman%20Mullick%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F9PyJRkvY2N4%3Fsi%3DCNb57CyOliMrajEH%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guest%20list%20at%20this%20144-year-old%20sweet%20shop%20has%20always%20been%20coloured.%20From%20journalists%2C%20the%20likes%20of%20Barkha%20Dutt%20and%20Prannoy%20Roy%3B%20and%20celebrities%2C%20the%20likes%20of%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%2C%20to%20legendary%20figures%20such%20as%20Ashutosh%20Mukherjee%20(a%20prominent%20Bengali%20educator)%20%E2%80%94%20everyone%20seems%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%